16
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,880
Ye Ying.

17
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:09,120
You sneaky woman.

18
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,560
We finally caught you.

19
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:13,080
Your Qingyun Gang messed with
the wrong people.

20
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,120
Our boss said that

21
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,160
you're all going down today!

22
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,400
Nonsense talking.

23
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:25,720
[Ye Ying,
Young Lady of Qingyun Gang]

24
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:46,160
♪I got fire in my veins♪

25
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,920
♪I got matches burning up♪

26
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,720
♪We're in a fighting♪

27
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,960
♪I'm gonna take it out♪

28
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,040
Inspector Huo.

29
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,920
What do you mean by this?

30
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,240
My Qingyun Gang

31
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,220
[Ye Hong, Leader of Qingyun Gang]
hasn't offended

32
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,200
the police lately, huh?

33
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,840
Whether you have or not

34
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,880
[Huo Xiao, Police Inspector]

35
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,160
depends on my mood today.

36
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,720
Just say what you want.

37
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,720
Ye Hong,

38
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,400
you know what I'm after.

39
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:38,280
Either hand it over today

40
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,240
or

41
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:42,640
Qingyun Gang disappears.

42
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:48,920
I've done plenty of favors
for you all these years.

43
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:51,800
And you still want to wipe me out.

44
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,200
Listen.

45
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,080
The Qingyun Gang isn't pushovers either!

46
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,160
So there's nothing more to say.

47
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,320
Miss,
why did you come back early?

48
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:19,920
The boss told us

49
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,000
to pick you up tonight.

50
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,240
I came back early
to surprise Dad.

51
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,160
Where's my dad?

52
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,200
What's going on?

53
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,880
Inspector Huo and the boss
went to the rooftop.

54
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,680
That man may want to
cause trouble again.

55
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,920
And asks for some benefit.

56
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,000
Which Inspector Huo?

57
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,800
Huo Xiao, Inspector Huo.

58
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,560
Dad!

59
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:52,600
Dad!

60
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,240
Dad!

61
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,240
Dad.

62
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,320
Huo Xiao.

63
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,440
I'll kill you!

64
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,600
[Dr. LOGY Pathology Lab]

65
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,360
An Ning.

66
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,600
[Mrs. Song]
The Song family is worth billions.

67
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,480
We need heirs.

68
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,800
[An Ning, 27, Not Pregnant]
What's the point of

69
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,560
marrying a barren wife like you?

70
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,200
Mom.

71
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,560
[An Ning]
The doctor said there's nothing

72
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,400
[Daughter-in-law of Song family]
wrong with me.

73
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,000
Watch your manners.

74
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,680
It's not your turn to talk
when elders are speaking.

75
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,080
Such an ill-mannered child.

76
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,280
Auntie.

77
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,360
Please don't be upset.

78
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,360
[Fang Yao, An Ning's friend]
An Ning's mother passed away early.

79
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,240
And her father also left recently.

80
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:36,760
It's understandable
she doesn't know these rules.

81
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,040
She's your daughter-in-law now.

82
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,560
Your guidance will mean a lot to her.

83
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,720
Fang Yao is right.

84
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,160
She came from an ordinary family.

85
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,240
No sense of proper manners.

86
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,320
I'll teach her some today.

87
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:56,880
An Ning.

88
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,880
Go get the soup.

89
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,160
Kneel.

90
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,560
Lift the soup above your head.

91
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,800
And bring it over on your knees.

92
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:29,080
Being a wife and daughter-in-law
in a wealthy family,

93
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:31,840
the most important thing is
to contribute to the household.

94
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,560
Since you can't bear children,

95
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,360
can't you at least
show respect to your in-laws?

96
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,040
An Ning.

97
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,880
Just do as auntie says.

98
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,280
Your parents passed away early.

99
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,480
Do you want people
to call you uneducated?

100
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,960
Or to badmouth your parents?

101
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,320
You can't even handle
such a small thing!

102
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,640
All you do is
embarrass the Song family.

103
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,560
What else can you even do?

104
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,200
Fang Yao!

105
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,720
You're my best friend.

106
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,760
How could you guys do this?

107
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,080
[Ti Cha, An Ning's husband]
What are you crying for?

108
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,920
I'm not dead yet!

109
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,200
Get out of here, now!

110
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,280
Don't ruin

111
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,480
my good moment.

112
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,480
An Ning.

113
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,240
This is your fault.

114
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,400
How could you mess up
your husband's mood?

115
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,960
You...

116
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,360
You...

117
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,360
I'll make you pay for this!

118
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,760
You dare hit me?

119
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,000
Get down on your knees!

120
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,920
I...

121
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,680
I'll finish you today!

122
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,160
A barren hen.

123
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,560
A jinx who brought misfortune
to your parents!

124
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,360
In bed, you're like a dead fish.

125
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,040
And now you want to tell me what to do?

126
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,560
Still crying, huh?

127
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,920
Tramp like you,
no one'd take even for free!

128
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,880
An Ning.

129
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,880
Your face is all bruised up.

130
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,120
Well,

131
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,960
shall I dab some medicine on you?

132
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,320
Come here.

133
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,040
Come on.

134
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,720
Go ahead.

135
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,600
Ti Cha.

136
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:04,160
Didn't you say An Ning
never makes a sound?

137
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:06,600
Doesn't she sound pretty when she does?

138
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,800
Not as nice as you do, though.

139
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,080
Look at her.

140
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:17,640
[Song Pa, An Ning's father-in-law]

141
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,160
She drove that car out?

142
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,240
The car was already tampered with.

143
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,240
She won't make it back today.

144
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:28,200
The An family's company
has long been mine.

145
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,640
[Brake system fault]
Leaving some shares to her daughter

146
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,080
won't change a thing.

147
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:34,120
It will all be mine eventually.

148
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,240
Huo Xiao.

149
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,120
I'm going to end you.

150
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,840
For my father's sake.

151
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,160
[Hospital]

152
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,160
Who are you?

153
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,160
Why am I here?

154
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,200
An Ning.

155
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,000
Don't think playing dumb

156
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:17,040
will get you out of
the trouble from the car crash.

157
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,360
A car crash?

158
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,680
How did I get into a car crash?

159
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,040
My head hurts so much.

160
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,160
Why does my head hurt so bad?

161
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,480
Why can't I remember anything?

162
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,440
An Ning.

163
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,640
That's enough.

164
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:37,840
An Ning?

165
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,240
Who's An Ning?

166
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,440
An Ning is you.

167
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,280
The useless waste.

168
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,520
Who are you?

169
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,640
How dare you call me a waste?

170
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:51,240
Because I'm your husband's mother.

171
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,360
Your mother-in-law.

172
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,160
How dare you talk back to me?

173
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,720
If I don't teach you a lesson today,

174
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,080
I've failed as your mother-in-law!

175
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,200
Running out in the middle of the night.

176
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,320
And stirring up so much trouble.

177
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,000
Why not just end it once and for all?

178
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,600
I...

179
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,440
You... you...

180
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:06,520
Mom.

181
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,280
Mom! Mom! Mom.

182
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:10,160
You poor girl with no family left.

183
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,920
You've really got some nerve, huh?

184
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,400
How dare you try to hit me!

185
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,800
Let... Let go of me!

186
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,720
Mom. Mom. Mom.

187
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,680
Are you okay, Mom?

188
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,360
Just drop dead!

189
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,160
Where did this crazy woman come from?

190
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,960
If you lose control again,

191
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:36,000
I won't mind breaking your other arm.

192
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:38,600
Mom.

193
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,240
Are you okay, Mom?

194
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,200
You mean woman.

195
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:45,360
You should take a look
at yourself first.

196
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,320
Who do you think
you are?

197
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,840
Daring to hit my mom.

198
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,240
Well, I finally get it now.

199
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,160
A spiteful mother-in-law

200
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,480
and her clingy son.

201
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:55,080
I must've been blind to
fall for your messed-up family.

202
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,880
An Ning.

203
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:58,200
I used to treat you like a punching bag.

204
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,920
You don't even dare to make a sound.

205
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,800
So what?

206
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,520
Did that car crash shake up
your whole personality?

207
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,480
Now,

208
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,600
get on your knees
and kowtow three times to me!

209
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,400
I'll

210
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,960
let you keep serving
the Song family!

211
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,680
You perfectly exemplify

212
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:15,800
what it means to be a brute.

213
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,240
All you do is insult women

214
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,640
to patch up your sad little pride.

215
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,880
Try being a decent person in this life.

216
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,240
In the next one,

217
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,560
being a fly

218
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,960
is the upper limit of
your reincarnation!

219
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,560
You... What are you doing?

220
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,520
Son! Son!

221
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,600
You...

222
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,200
Son!

223
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,320
- You're not An Ning
- It hurts!

224
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,720
What do you mean?

225
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,280
Then who am I?

226
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,560
Your words and actions

227
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:38,160
don't match her at all.

228
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,280
So that question

229
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,720
should be mine to ask you.

230
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:43,880
Mr. Song,

231
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,000
after consulting with specialists,

232
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,080
we believe your daughter-in-law suffered
severe head trauma,

233
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,560
which caused retrograde amnesia.

234
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:50,560
It might lead to
major personality changes.

235
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:52,120
How long will it take for me to regain
my memory?

236
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,920
Hard to say.

237
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,320
But familiar people and places

238
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,720
could help trigger your memory.

239
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,720
However,

240
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,200
do either of your arms...

241
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,400
No need.

242
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,640
I don't trust any of you.

243
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,280
Until my memory comes back,

244
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,440
I'll request 24-hour police protection.

245
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,440
You've come just in time.

246
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,320
Since coming back with you,

247
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,800
I realized all the wrongs
you've done to me before.

248
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,960
The police are on their way.

249
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,320
Please explain yourselves clearly.

